    "text": [
        "In some previous eras, people are travelling too much in foreign countries because  the rate of travelling cost is declining day by day.This happens due to numerous reasons and has various merits and demerits which will be discussed in the below paragraphs.",
        "To begin with,the major benefit of this development is , first and foremost, the expenses of flight are less expensive so that ,all kinds of categories can effort their rates.All classes of people can fly to other countries compared to the previous period.Now people flying in overseas for many reasons it including for study , business and as a tourist.but it is possible because  it is not costly.In addition, another maritdof this Trend. It is more profitable for businessmen to improve their business in foreign countries now they make a transaction very easily and they do not get any burden of cost and losses in the business.They improve their business with new foreign techniques and knowledge",
